	<div class="perex-content"><p>變異檢測（variant calling）是基因組學研究中的關鍵步驟，主要區分<strong>生殖系變異（germline variants）<strong>與</strong>體細胞變異（somatic variants）</strong>。 Variant calling is a crucial step in genomic research, primarily distinguishing between <strong style="font-size: 1.075rem; letter-spacing: 0px;">germline variants</strong> and <strong style="font-size: 1.075rem; letter-spacing: 0px;">somatic variants</strong>.</p></div>
